response.overview: Two Door Cinema Club Live performance at Reading Festival 2012. Set list included Cigarettes in the Theatre, Undercover Martyn, Do You Want It All?, This Is the Life, Wake Up, Sleep Alone, Next Year, Something Good Can Work, Handshake, Eat That Up, It's Good for You, What You Know, Someday, Come Back Home and I Can Talk
